<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich X. von Plauen, Herr zu Königswart</head><p>Der Rat bedauert, dass ein Turm mit Kriegsgerät des Adressaten abgebrannt ist, und teilt mit, dass er trotz widriger Umstände eine Tonne Salpeter kaufen und gen Eger schicken wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_467" id="232v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_467_r2l21"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Plawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l22"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu küngſwart </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_467_r2l23">Edler lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / als vns eẅr edel <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat wıe eẅch ſchad </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l24">geſchehen vnd ein turn mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> gereͣte awſʒgeprant ſey etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l25"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd ıſt vns <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell ſchad laıd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l26">Als Jr vns denn <expan>gepette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel <expan>ſalpet<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns aufʒu = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l27"><expan>brıng<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ʒu ſchıken etc / <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ewr edel <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l28">ſelbs ſölıchs ʒeẅgs vnd gereͣts niht <expan>enhabe<ex>n</ex></expan> / denn des wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l29">teglıchen ʒu <expan>vnſer<ex>r</ex></expan> ſtat notdurft bedurffen . ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l30">auch daʒ <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> nıht vıl <expan>ſalpet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> bey vns faıl ſey . wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_467_r2l31">ſo haben wır doch beſtellet . ein <expan>tunne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſalpet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> bey vns ʒu </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_468" id="233r"/><ab facs="#facs_468_r2l2">kawffen . da mıt wır eẅr edel eren vnd dıe ſchenken wellen . 
<add><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l1">vnd dıe </ab><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l2">gen Eger </ab><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l3">ſchıcken ſo </ab><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l4">vvir erſt </ab><ab facs="#facs_468_r1l5">mügen </ab></add>
<del rend="crossout">wurdt </del></ab><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_468_r2l4">Jr denn ʒurat daʒ Jr <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_468_r2l3">edell </ab></add> mer <expan>ſalpet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>kawffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_468_r2l5">wöltet . darinn <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> edel </del> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</del><ab facs="#facs_468_r2l6">
<del rend="crossout"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beweıſen</del> Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab><ab facs="#facs_468_r2l7"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_467" id="232v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Plawen, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        zu Küngswart</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr edel
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie ewch schad geschehen
                        und ein turn mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> gereͣte awszgeprant sey etc.,
                        das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und ist uns <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell schad laid. Als ir uns denn
                                <expan>gepette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        edel <expan>salpet<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns
                            <expan>aufzubring<ex>en</ex></expan> und zu schiken etc.,
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr edel
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir selbs sölichs zewgs und gereͣts
                        niht <expan>enhabe<ex>n</ex></expan>, denn des wir teglichen zu
                                <expan>unser<ex>r</ex></expan> stat notdurft bedurffen. So
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wir auch, daz
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> niht vil
                            <expan>salpet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> bey uns fail sey; wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so haben wir doch bestellet ein
                                <expan>tunne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>salpet<ex>er</ex>s</expan> bey uns zu <pb facs="#facs_468" id="233r"/>kawffen,
                        damit wir ewr edel eren und die schenken wellen <add>und die gen Eger
                            schicken, so wir erst mügen</add>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                        <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
